    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/855f020df51e0e415d727f7784d1e2f7.poster.avif?t=1770336113\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/855f020df51e0e415d727f7784d1e2f7.webm?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/855f020df51e0e415d727f7784d1e2f7.mp4?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新刺激的动作益智体验！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Kyubu Kyubu Dice》的世界！这是一款上手简单、精通有挑战的动作益智游戏！掷出你的魔法骰子，将其颜色与舞台上出现的面板匹配。每一次掷骰都是对你反应速度和预判能力的考验，游戏时间越长，节奏就越紧张！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作适合各个年龄段的玩家，无论是单人游戏还是与朋友一起联机对战都能获得乐趣！考验你的空间思维，挑战自己，在每一步中做好计划。多种游戏模式等你探索，每次游玩都有全新体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/8aff0b4b216abc735a332de5778795da.poster.avif?t=1770336113\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/8aff0b4b216abc735a332de5778795da.webm?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/8aff0b4b216abc735a332de5778795da.mp4?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>各具特色的角色阵容！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中登场的是一群富有魅力的角色，每位角色都以可爱的日系动漫风格精心设计，完美契合游戏的整体氛围。从活泼开朗到冷静神秘，每个角色都有鲜明的个性。更棒的是，所有角色都配有<strong>日语语音</strong>，让你享受原汁原味的动漫式游戏体验！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/c16ab72bb20dedf113a0237810643362.poster.avif?t=1770336113\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/c16ab72bb20dedf113a0237810643362.webm?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/c16ab72bb20dedf113a0237810643362.mp4?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>对战模式等你来战！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想和朋友一决高下，看看谁才是真正的强者？加入多人对战模式，迅速思考、巧妙出招就是胜利关键！你可以进行1对1对战，也可以比拼高分排名。无论是冲击排行榜还是轻松游玩，都能找到适合自己的模式。尝试不同的规则和策略，每一局都是全新的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/7b3ab83552638ea7e0ce17ac159f55cd.poster.avif?t=1770336113\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/7b3ab83552638ea7e0ce17ac159f55cd.webm?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234170/extras/7b3ab83552638ea7e0ce17ac159f55cd.mp4?t=1770336113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入愿望单并关注我们获取更多更新！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Kyubu Kyubu Dice》仍在开发中，正式版将带来更多丰富内容！现在就将本作加入你的<strong>愿望单</strong>，并关注游戏，第一时间获取最新资讯！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲✨永远记住 —— 你最棒！</p>",
